<P>
4 SOCCER TEAMS PLAY AT COLISEUM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By CHRIS BAKER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The national soccer teams of El Salvador, Guatemala, Chile and Paraguay will 
compete in a tournament this weekend at the Coliseum. Chile will play Guatemala 
tonight at 7, and El Salvador will take on Paraguay at 9. Sunday, Guatemala 
will face Paraguay at 4:30 p.m., and El Salvador will meet Chile at 6:30. CHRIS 
BAKER 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA050589-0033 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 52861 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 5, 1989, Friday, Southland Edition 
</P>
