<P>
Photo, Smooth sailing -- Feltina Means of Van Nuys High, who won four events in 
the Valley Pac-8 Conference track finals Thursday, clears the last hurdle en 
route to a 47.5 finish in the 300-meter hurdles. BOB CAREY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
