<P>
SUITS; BREACH OF CONTRACT; STUDENT LOANS; BANK OF AMERICA; CALIFORNIA STUDENT 
LOAN FINANCE CORP; FIRST INDEPENDENT TRUST CO; FRAUD 
</P>
