in photo at far left exhort schoolchildren to "just say no" to drug use. ; 
Photo, Schoolchildren from throughout Los Angeles County enthusiastically 
participate in Just Say No rally held at Rose Bowl. JOSE GALVEZ / Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
