Environmental engineer Mary Cleave ; Photo, Medical Doctor Norman Thagard ; 
Photo, Air Force Major Mark Lee ; Photo, Space Shuttle ; Photo, Onward and 
upward -- The Atlantis crew -- from left, Ronald Grabe, Norman Thagard 
(waving), Mary Cleave, commander David Walker and Mark Lee -- as they walked to 
the shuttle in Florida Thursday, and the fiery blastoff. United Press 
International Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
ATLANTIS (SPACE SHUTTLE); SPACE PROGRAMS -- UNITED STATES; SPACE SHUTTLE; SPACE 
EXPLORATION; MAGELLAN VENUS RADAR MAPPER (SPACECRAFT) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
