IRAN; UNITED STATES -- MILITARY AID -- HONDURAS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN 
RELATIONS -- HONDURAS; GUERRILLAS -- NICARAGUA; BUSH, GEORGE; REAGAN, RONALD; 
NORTH, OLIVER L 
</P>
