<P>
WRITERS; VANDENBURGH, JANE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA050589-0114 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 53062 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 5, 1989, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
